Lady Bird Lemon Bundt Cake
  --Nordic Ware

1 c butter
1 2/3 c sugar
10 egg yolks, lightly beaten
3 1/4 c flour
4 tsp baking powder
1/2 tsp salt
1 c milk
1 tsp vanilla 
1 tsp grated lemon peel
1 1/2 tbsp lemon juice

Heat oven to 325F. Grease and flour a 10 or 12 c bundt pan. In large bowl, cream butter and sugar until light and fluffy. Add beaten egg yolks until incorporated. Sift together flour, baking powder and salt; resift 3 times. Add to butter mixture, alternating with milk. Mix until incorporated. Add vanilla, lemon peel and lemon juice. Beat 2 min. Bake for 1 hr, or until cake tester comes out clean. Cool in pan for 10 min. Invert on wire rack or serving platter to complete cooling. Sprinkle top with confectionersâ€™ sugar if desired.

